# 🛒 Market Basket Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview
This project performs Market Basket Analysis using association rule learning to identify relationships between products.

## 🎯 Objective
To discover patterns in customer purchasing behavior and generate actionable insights.

## 📂 Dataset
- Groceries dataset
- Transactions with multiple items

## ⚙️ Tools & Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- Mlxtend
- Jupyter Notebook

## 🧠 Techniques Used
- Apriori Algorithm
- Association Rule Mining

## 📊 Key Metrics
- Support
- Confidence
- Lift

## 📈 Results
- Identified frequently purchased itemsets
- Generated association rules
- Provided business insights for cross-selling

